{"tid":453604,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"突然醒悟沒有朋友的原因！","createTime":"2017-10-31T10:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T12:39:04.000Z","uid":5921,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"98745f2f8965f6217e1b7910e9c74faddc871623","tid":453604,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"近墨者黑 無友不如己者<br />\n依啲說話聽得多<br />\n岩岩諗起 原來是真理<br />\n因為自己太差<br />\n會drag down人<br />\n人地對人生充滿希望同動力 我做佢朋友就會拖低佢 降低佢質素<br />\n唔怪得無人做我朋友 <br />\n我終於醒悟了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最重要的是心態！要努力過生活！要拚命去生存！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無朋友個啲都要時刻諗吓自己有咩不足！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日怨天尤人是無用的！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e5865b0ea3fb133f76ed2321319b5beda7d92f","tid":453604,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:33:45.000Z","msg":"補救？"},{"pid":"cb2ffe1db27b4cf71f007187a1ea38c59204215d","tid":453604,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:37:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補救？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39741bba8b5e82181210396d7b5a3c03e8a24f25","tid":453604,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:37:49.000Z","msg":"恭喜你諗通左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c59bea34fdc3d6df5769f92755424e4d180313d","tid":453604,"uid":92278,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:37:55.000Z","msg":"最憎啲正能量撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4453c7a41f86b374ae310ecc71870a25cdae0155","tid":453604,"uid":178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:52:47.000Z","msg":"冇發過負能量但都係完